flowchart LR
  A[Documents] --> B[Tokenizer]
  B --> C[Vocabulary]
  C --> D[TF-IDF Matrix]
  D --> E[SVD / Latent Projection]
  E --> F[(Local Vectors)]
  G[Query] --> H[Same tokenizer + vocabulary]
  H --> I[Query TF-IDF]
  I --> J[Same projection]
  J --> K[Query Vector]
  F --> L[Cosine Ranking]
  K --> L
  L --> M[Traceable Results]
